Visualizer
1,	https://github.com/o-reo/push_swap_visualizer

2,	In a selected folder, git clone into a folder called visualizer
	git clone https://github.com/o-reo/push_swap_visualizer visualizer

3,	fish (if you want interactive shell)

4,	ls
5, 	cd visualizer
6,	ls
7,	we have already installed gcc, so skip Install c++ compiler

8,	cmake --version
	cmake is also already installed

9,	mkdir build
10,	cd build
11,	cmake -DCMAKE_C_COMPILER=/usr/bin/gcc -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=/us/bin/g++ ..
12,	ls
13,	make

14,	./bin/visualizer

15,	visualizer will open 3 windows - values, control and commands
	select the folder where you placed your push_swap
	this is done by moving 1 or 2 levels up or down the current folder

